trans-unit.source: This binding element can be used to enable [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] applications to send messages to and receive messages from existing MSMQ applications that use either COM, MSMQ native APIs, or the APIs in <xref href="System.Messaging"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Denne bindingselement kan brukes til å aktivere [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programmer for å sende meldinger til eller motta meldinger fra eksisterende MSMQ-programmer som bruker COM, opprinnelig MSMQ-APIer eller API-er i <xref href="System.Messaging"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use this class to send and receive messages from MSMQ-based messaging applications.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne klassen til å sende eller motta meldinger fra MSMQ-baserte meldingsprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: This property returns the string "msmq.formatname" to indicate the addressing scheme used by the MSMQ integration channel.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer strengen "msmq.formatname" til å angi adresseringsskjemaet brukes av kanalen for MSMQ-integrering.

trans-unit.source: For more information about queue addressing, see [Service Endpoints and Queue Addressing](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om køen adressering, se [Service sluttpunkt og køen adressering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"></xref> to be used when serializing MSMQ messages.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"> </xref> som skal brukes under serialisering av MSMQ-meldinger.

trans-unit.source: This property can have one of the following values: - `ActiveX` - The ActiveX serializer is used to serialize objects.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan ha én av følgende verdier:- `ActiveX` -egenskapen ActiveX serialisering brukes til å serialisere objekter.

trans-unit.source: - `Binary` - The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.Formatters.Binary.BinaryFormatter> is used to serialize objects.
- `ByteArray` - The object is serialized to an array of bytes.
- `Stream` - The object is serialized to a stream.
- `Xml` - The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> is used to serialize objects.
- The default value is `Xml`.
The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"></xref> to be used when serializing MSMQ messages.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"> </xref> som skal brukes under serialisering av MSMQ-meldinger.

trans-unit.source: The value is not within the values of <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien er ikke innenfor verdiene i <xref href="System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an array of <xref:System.Type> objects that contain the types to which messages should be deserialized.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en matrise av <xref:System.Type>objekter som inneholder typen meldinger må deserialiseres.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The body of an MSMQ message is not typed.
trans-unit.target: Meldingsteksten i et MSMQ-melding er skrevet inn.

trans-unit.source: The TargetSerializationTypes property enables you to specify the types to which messages are deserialized when they are sent from an MSMQ application to a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] receiving application.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TargetSerializationTypes kan du angi typene som meldinger deserialiseres når de er sendt fra et MSMQ-program til en [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] mottak av programmet.

trans-unit.source: This property is used only if <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat> is set to `Xml`.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen brukes bare hvis <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat>er satt til `Xml`.</xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqIntegration.MsmqMessageSerializationFormat>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Type> that contains the types to which messages should be deserialized.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Type>som inneholder typen meldinger må deserialiseres.</xref:System.Type>
